So it's not going to happen overnight, but it will happen over time. And remind me your first question. Occupancy. Oh, thank you.

So look, I think we're still on track to achieve our goal. I mean I -- frankly, I think we've done an unbelievable job in increasing our occupancy and increasing our cash flow since the shutdowns. So hopefully, in '23, we'll get back to pre-COVID levels.

