So it's kind of counterintuitive. But again, I'm not looking forward. I don't want a recession. I hope there's not a recession.

But from the standpoint of redevelopment and new development, we actually counter -- the countercyclicality of cost of construction may actually be one of the side benefits that we can take advantage of.

